node.text:
Each and every week we'll be giving away $500 to one lucky person that ordered from GasMonkeyGarage.com and entered the giveaway! Who is taking home the first $500? Could it be you? Watch and see! 

How can you enter to win? It's simple, for every $1 you spend at GasMonkeyGarage.com gets you 1 entry to win not only one of my cars but also the weekly prize of $500! 

Don't worry, if you didn't win this week, you still have a chance to win the grand prize and $500 next week. 

#GasMonkeyGarage #GasMonkey #RichardRawlings #Giveaway #Sweepstakes #Prize #Win

node.text:
Life gets tough for all of us at some point. When I saw a fan wearing a Gas Monkey tee in court and facing eviction, we knew that he needed to step in and help not just Luis but the property owner as well. Let's be honest, times have been tough for both sides!

If you've ever worn a Gas Monkey Garage shirt or watched one of our videos, you're apart of the Gas Monkey family, and without sounding too much like Dominic Toretto, family has to look out for each other! 

#GasMonkeyGarage #GasMonkey #RichardRawlings #FastNLoud

node.title: Saving a Gas Monkey fan from EVICTION!

node.text:
I’m ecstatic to announce that I’ll be the celebrity guest judge for this years virtual Fat Guys Car Show! If you’re in the Thunderbay, Canada area, you can enter your pride and joy into this virtual car show and win one of many cash prizes, with best-show winning $1,000!

I just wonder, why was I chose for the Fat Guys Car Show? 🤔

If you want to get in on the fun, register for the 10th Annual @fatguysautoparts car show today at FatGuysCarShow.com

node.text:
My largest purchase EVER of 200+ motorcycles is getting closer and closer to auction, and  I want show some love to just some of the gems in this incredible collection. This 1973 Kawasaki H-1 is one of my absolute favorites and it shows incredibly low mileage! 

Be sure to check out all of the other incredible motorcycles, cars, and memorabilia collected by the legendary flat track racer, Danny "Kannonball" Kannenberg, that is headed to auction soon on September 10th and 11th.

For more information and to register to bid, head to bit.ly/GMG-KANNENBERG-COLLECTION or WorldWideAuctioneers.com now! LINK IN BIO. 

#motorcycles #motorbike #kawasaki #suzuki #yamaha #ducati #ktm #motorcycle #instamotogallery #bikestagram

Between finding Pontiac GTO heaven and cleaning out the 230+ motorcycle nest, I’ve stumbled upon some gold again! Watch a new episode of Wheels & Deals on our YouTube Channel. Link in bio.

With a collector looking to get rid of 60+ classic cars scattered all across Minnesota in barn, I’m sure I can strike a deal. Watch and see!

#GasMonkeyGarage #GasMonkey #RichardRawlings #ClassicCars #Cars #Carporn #Vintagecars #car

node.text:
Each and every week we'll be giving away $500 to one lucky person that ordered from GasMonkeyGarage.com and entered the giveaway! Who is taking home the first $500? Could it be you? Watch and see! 

How can you enter to win? It's simple, for every $1 you spend at GasMonkeyGarage.com gets you 1 entry to win not only one of my cars but also the weekly prize of $500! 

Don't worry, if you didn't win this week, you still have a chance to win the grand prize and $500 next week. 

#GasMonkeyGarage #GasMonkey #RichardRawlings #Giveaway #Sweepstakes #Prize #Win
